<COL 78f5ff>"Board Quests" ae available!</COL>
In various locations you will see <COL
ffdc78>"Quest Boards"</COL>
Residents make their various requests with
<COL ffdc78>"Board Quests"</COL> Every day we
get new requests.
<COL ffdc78>"Elimination Quests"</COL> and <COL
ffdc78>"Delivery Quests"</COL>,
Choose whichever you like.

<COL ffdc78>"Elimination Quests" are aimed at the
suppression of monsters The target enemies are
indicated
by a green circle on the mini map</COL>
<COL ffdc78>"Delivery Quests" are about obtaining
specific items
and deliver them to a "Delivery Box"</COL>
However, if the time limit for the delivery has
passed,
the quest will automatically fail.
Please be careful.
